snippet.title: Fall Guys Satellite Scramble Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the official Fall Guys Satellite Scramble Gameplay Trailer. For more details on Season 2 of Fall Guys, visit https://www.fallguys.com/seasons/season-2

With Fall Guys having a fancy new season in space, we had to bring you some delightfully galactic rounds and obstacles! Jump through the space time level continuum with us and take a sneak peek at each of them!

Here's the Fall Guys Satellite Scramble Announcement Blog: https://www.fallguys.com/news/fall-guys-season-2-satellite-scramble-announcement

For all the latest Fall Guys news, including drop dates for Limited Time Events, store items and collaborations, head on over to our official social channels!
